該大學規模較小，在學本科生約有2,000人，此外300多人就讀法學院。其2018年在全美文理學院中排在第10位<ref>{{cite web |url=http://colleges.usnews.rankingsandreviews.com/best-colleges/washington-and-lee-university-234207/overall-rankings |title=Washington and Lee University Overall Rankings Best Colleges US News |publisher=Colleges.usnews.rankingsandreviews.com |accessdate=2016-09-09 |archive-date=2016-07-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160723083305/http://colleges.usnews.rankingsandreviews.com/best-colleges/washington-and-lee-university-234207/overall-rankings |dead-url=no }}</ref>，法學院則排在全國31位。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://grad-schools.usnews.rankingsandreviews.com/best-graduate-schools/top-law-schools/law-rankings/page+2 |title=America's Graduate Schools 2016: Best Law Schools |publisher=Colleges.usnews.rankingsandreviews.com |date=2015-03-10 |accessdate=2016-02-24 |archive-date=2015-02-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150227083247/http://grad-schools.usnews.rankingsandreviews.com/best-graduate-schools/top-law-schools/law-rankings/page+2 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

該大學下分三個學院，即The College（全部本科生第一年都就讀於此）、威廉姆斯商業、經濟和政治學院（Williams School of Commerce, Economics, and Politics）和法學院（School of Law），所提供的本科學位約40個，輔修學位約30個。2018年的錄取率為24%。

